channel.description: Everytime i copy something from a forum for like lets a kalphite area or taverly it makes me change the cfg file to a txt file and I know it not suppose to change. also the text is usually bigger and in a diffrent font. Even if i change it exactly how the rest of the file is it doesnt work. BTW i use notepad and WordPad. Maybe theres a better program to use. Any help would be greatly appreicated
